","tid":828261,"uid":161168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"989693c3450613f0e67079373b4d0f4f9699bf06","tid":828261,"uid":37586,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"61557e18ff0254242f42b3592a161d6e9afbdfa9","tid":828261,"uid":42921,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"ea122eac001d29f32cc2571bf1ee41e1a6d8edfa","tid":828261,"uid":511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:24:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:25:57.000Z","msg":"支拿人先會自high <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:30:29.000Z","msg":"死都拗返生乃支那特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T03:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79112dbb0b512c899f918ceb0db4be96aab14da1","tid":828261,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:44:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e708624481b947f0ec2c7c4014dcbab2f11b31d","tid":828261,"uid":33668,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T06:55:34.000Z","msg":"我落嚟撲奶粉 = 落嚟消費救香港<br />\n<br />\n我吐現撲水 = 我量劍衝擊美國經濟<br />\n<br />\nGOODEST LOGIC"},{"pid":"a7292b5406f946229226bf82443ab770b80ade66","tid":828261,"uid":198175,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:10:37.000Z","msg":"沽美債, 買返国企民企H股係海外發行的美元債券, 左手換右手幫自己散水, 咁都算係美元外滙儲備喎.<br />\n<br />\n近排玩所謂逆周期因子去干預人仔開市價, 咪又係一開市就mark高人仔然後用美元真金白銀咁去托市, 咁D美元邊度嚟呢, 借到盡頭就要動用外滙儲備老本中的美債.<br />\n<br />\n唔係佢真心要放核彈, 係7到盡頭冇得揀啫."},{"pid":"dd38432e6b2409173b87cd5445713563ca8b8465","tid":828261,"uid":65128,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09