美元，6月淨流入規模由1145億美元上修至1897億美元。在這一背景下，中國卻反而減持美債，引發市場的關注。</span></blockquote><br />\n77/10000連1%都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等支那估出10%先講喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅字咪人棄我取囉, 美國加息美元萬劍歸宗之際你夠膽放人地咪等執平貨囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"869f39c522490e74c903de324e711e20392f37c1","tid":828261,"uid":194302,"like":1,"dislike":17,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"106cbb84ce6e186fd8c4d03d332a17bd81bf7139","tid":828261,"uid":42921,"like":55,"dislike":0,"score":55,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:23:57.000Z","msg":"無錢要套現就話拋售，笑死人"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:05:54.000Z","msg":"你知唔知中國有幾多外匯儲備？"},{"pid":"8163db1dc1e966230be500e47b0bb26a4d90d65f","tid":828261,"uid":194302,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"5ff332a3e7e6aa3053ea4a60109451e9375b735e","tid":828261,"uid":55951,"like":31,"dislike":1,"score":30,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T14:32:48.000Z","msg":"你一放，大把國家接<br />\n歐盟、日本、俄羅斯一定會接<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T02:11:05.000Z","msg":"歐盟同日本都窮都pk, 俄羅斯會接咁都比你諗到， 好野"},{"pid":"8d888345ae327adc6e442a7a29e57e19a35a87fb","tid":828261,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8163db1dc1e966230be500e47b0bb26a4d90d65f","tid":828261,"uid":194302,"like":1,"dislike":15,"score":-14,"quote":{"pid":"5ff