1.1682萬億美元；而且當月持倉按月減少77億美元，減持規模為1月以來最大。<br />\n<br />\n至於被海外視為中國持有美債離岸中介的比利時，7月持倉排在第12位，當月持倉也減少2億美元，為四個月來首度減持，6月增持42億美元。<br />\n<br />\n值得注意的是，<span style=\"color: red;\">從總體數據看，美債需求其實正在回升，7月海外投資者淨買入美國資產、即國際資本淨流入為552億美元，6月淨流入規模由1145億美元上修至1897億美元。在這一背景下，中國卻反而減持美債，引發市場的關注。</span></blockquote><br />\n77/10000連1%都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等支那估出10%先講喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n紅字咪人棄我取囉, 美國加息美元萬劍歸宗之際你夠膽放人地咪等執平貨囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:02:57.000Z","msg":"根本冇得同美國玩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已發展國家唔會比美債跌  一定局住買"},{"pid":"0977c77a2f21663a26808a314df7725995dbd5f5","tid":828261,"uid":38316,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:06:57.000Z","msg":"大陸班官成副身家喺晒美國<br />\n邊會有心想美國死"},{"pid":"c9814bda1305e558a514425cb9c9d892e0a7068c","tid":828261,"uid":36820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"抛完就人仔爆"},{"pid":"67d6018835758ad4f9665a038f00e10f528390a6","tid":828261,"uid":164730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:10:50.000Z","msg":"中共殺敵一百，自傷一千 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1294713604b8d5b736011f0f6c8c45