非常時期，美國可根據啟動這項緊急法案，凍結中國持有的美國國債，甚至一筆勾銷美國對中國的欠債。<br />\n啟動《國際緊急經濟權力法案》，也就是宣佈美國全國進入貿易緊急狀態，和中國在貿易這個戰場上來一場生死戰"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:46:48.000Z","msg":"英女皇夠有法律權力去拒簽法案啦，但佢唔會用丫嘛。因為無人會首先去破壞個平衡。<br />\n<br />\n係強國人先會有權用突呢個概念。"},{"pid":"d2ecb9591d597eac2f87a1c9955c7a5298a61d7f","tid":828261,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b3690a6978fc34e0bd57769b2e30e65b7ee902f","tid":828261,"uid":185884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28341c83d95df80f3ab9fc04d3bffe9f6a3fcb24","tid":828261,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"826f11038a159bd4a03aa5f98e027d5d0900b274","tid":828261,"uid":194302,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T03:02:03.000Z","msg":"得閒睇多d新聞，讀多d書啦， 唔係一句on9就得架， 傻西"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"都唔係一句「睇多啲新聞就」就證明你有point架柒碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日話人無錢，十足茶樓啲廢老咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知仲以為歐盟同日本變咗第三世界<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:06:52.000Z","msg":"佢睇抆匪太<br />\n身痕亂播"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:54:06.000Z","msg":"屌啲支那人邏輯好簡單，佢哋覺得支那仆街等於全世界都仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60601702b3f108b2f9cccbd2192e77adba6c4c08","tid":828261,"uid":185884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2ecb9591d597eac2f87a1c9955c7a5298a61d7f","tid":828261,"uid":55951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4b3690a6978fc34e0bd57769b2e30e65b7ee902f","tid":828261,"uid":185884,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"28341c83d95df80f3ab9fc04d3bffe9f6a3fcb24","tid":828261,"uid":57376,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-09-22T04:05:49.000Z","msg":"都唔係一句「睇多啲新聞就」就證明你有point架柒碌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日話人無錢，十足茶樓啲廢老咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />